}
Node "Sara_3_2a_3b_2a"
notes "Deduct eight caps from the PC's inventory. Add one Iguana-on-a-stick to the PC's inventory."
{
NPCText "Okay. *She walks over to a rack of cooking sticks, which are sweating slowly over a low fire. She picks one up, being careful not to burn her fingers on the greasy chunks of meat on it, and brings it over to you.\" Here you are. Mind, it's still pretty hot."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So what can you tell me about Crossroads?" linkto "Sara_4_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I could use a drink, now." linkto "Sara_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I could still use some more food. What do you have on offer again?" linkto "Sara_3_2a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to be going, now." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "More food. More." linkto "Sara_3_2a_2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Now want drink." linkto "Sara_1a_2D_2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I go." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Sara_3_2a_3b_2b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hmm. You might want to try the jerky, then."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay. How much is that?" linkto "Sara_3_2a_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, I think I'd prefer a drink." linkto "Sara_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll get something another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Sara_3_2b_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Water's two caps a mug."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You want me to pay for water?" linkto "Sara_3_2b_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Here's the two caps." linkto "Sara_3_2b_2b" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 2 link_next NONE } notes "Deduct two caps from the PC's inventory."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry, I can't even afford that." linkto "Sara_3_2b_2c" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps < 2 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, hold the drink. I have to be going." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- PAY -" linkto "Sara_3_2b_2b" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 2 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- LEAVE -" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Sara_3_2b_2a_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Of course. We don't bring it in all the way from Rusty Springs just to give it away. You got two caps or not?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Here's the two caps." linkto "Sara_3_2b_2b" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 2 link_next NONE } notes "Deduct two caps from the PC's inventory."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry, I can't even afford that." linkto "Sara_3_2b_2c" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps < 2 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where's Rusty Springs?" linkto "Sara_3_2b_2a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, hold the drink. I have to be going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Sara_3_2b_2a_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You don't know where Rusty Springs is? *She looks surprised.* Go ask one of the caravan guys who run there. They'll tell you all about it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Here's two caps for the water." linkto "Sara_3_2b_2b" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps >= 2 link_next NONE } notes "Deduct two caps from the PC's inventory."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry, I can't even afford two caps for the water." linkto "Sara_3_2b_2c" conditions { CHECK_MONEY dude_caps < 2 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, hold the drink. I have to be going." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Sara_3_2b_2b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Here you go. *She puts an earthenware mug filled with clean-looking water in front of you. You drink it.\""
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So what can you tell me about Crossroads?" linkto "Sara_4_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I could use another drink." linkto "Sara_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you have in the way of food?" linkto "Sara_3_2a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to be going, now." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "More drink." linkto "Sara_1a_2D_2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Food, now." linkto "Sara_3_2a_2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Burp.* Hah! 'Bye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Sara_3_2b_2c"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Ah, hell. I can't have you dying of thirst. Come on, this one's on me."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks!" linkto "Sara_3_2b_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, if water costs two caps, I'll go and earn them. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
