Node "Sara_4_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Crossroads is a decent enough place to live. There's plenty of thirsty mouths around, so I'm never short of business. If you want the full low-down on the place, though, you should go see Old Man Rich. What he doesn't know about Crossroads ain't worth knowing."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where can I find Old Man Rich?" linkto "Sara_4_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I could use another drink." linkto "Sara_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What are you serving in the way of food?" linkto "Sara_3_2a_2"  notes ""
              }
}
